description: This simple traybake is light and perfect for summer evenings.
name: Cod, Lemon & Fennel Traybake Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 1 bulb fennel, trimmed and sliced, fronds reserved
2 medium red onions, peeled and sliced
2 medium lemons, thinly sliced into rounds

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat the oven to 180Â°C. Place the vegetables and lemon slices in a large roasting tin and toss in a tablespoon of oil. Spread out in a single layer and roast for 45 minutes.
Place the fish fillets on top of the vegetables, season with black pepper and place back in the oven for 1215 minutes, until the cod is cooked through.
Serve with parsley and fennel fronds on top.
